{"tid":230812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"6/5 傑志vs西方 港超\"反西方\"聯合軍 通告","createTime":"2017-05-05T15:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T17:38:12.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5b8b484eaaa47d491be87833c71d0ed78c7a82","tid":230812,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"港超&quot;反西方&quot;聯合軍通告<br />\n<br />\n有睇開港超都知西方呢隊波今季點樣出賣香港<br />\n如果到而家都唔知，我都費事哂口水解釋<br />\n<br />\n6/5場波<br />\n傑志打氣區係28區(近界限街）<br />\n大家可以去28區幫手打氣<br />\n如果滿咗<br />\n可以去27,29或30區<br />\n<br />\n其實坐邊區唔係最緊要<br />\n最重要係盡一切力量去令到西方輸波<br />\n總之一見西方掂波就噓就屌<br />\n見傑志掂波就打氣加掌聲<br />\n唔好再俾機會西方出賣香港人"},{"pid":"612c8cf24172780cfa9fb75b56fcad71dc8e60db","tid":230812,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/232511_d4bce1eed8a6a67ebfa502c164a768da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F232511_d4bce1eed8a6a67ebfa502c164a768da.jpg&h=ba8e8d91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7576277686672c345e8dd43fb636a7240bca2d6","tid":230812,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b30ea21235d8f6df4a31e90360673daa655d8adb","tid":230812,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}